  </p>

  <h2>Intellectual property</h2>
  <p>
    Unless otherwise stated, the WorthCalc name, branding, page design, and
    calculator code belong to the site operator. You retain responsibility
    for any content or figures you type into a calculator; since calculators
    run in your browser, that content is never transmitted to us in the
    first place.
  </p>

  <h2>Advertising</h2>
  <p>
    WorthCalc is supported by advertising, including Google AdSense. Ads may
    be shown alongside calculator results. Advertisers are solely responsible
    for the content of their own ads.
  </p>

